inclusion_criteria:
1.used a vertex-based method to estimate whole-brain cortical thickness changes in MDD;
2.compared patients with MDD to HCs;
3.examined adults, excluding individuals >65 years or <18 years old;
4.were limited to medication-free patients, who either had never received anti-depressant medication (i.e. were medication-naive) or who were previously treated but drug free for at least 7 days prior to MRI scanning;
5.provided the effect coordinates of significant clusters in Montreal Neurological Institute (MNI) or Talairach space."
